      "span_text": "Alternatively, cells (1ˆ10 For cell cycle analysis, osteoclast progenitors were incubated in culture medium with or without M-CSF (30 ng/mL) for 12 h and were then detached from the plate by exposure to trypsin and isolated by centrifugation at 1000ˆg for 5 min."
